snippet.title: Resident Evil - GameBoy Color - Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Here is a Walkthrough for the cancelled Resident Evil Gameboy Color game.

This game is only 90% complete, so I'll go as far as I can.
 
Here's a link to the ROM of the game:

http://depositfiles.com/files/y84l1gk6k
